com.luigisgro.cqf.fdm
Interface Grid

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseGrid, FullGrid, TwoStepsGrid
public interface Grid

Finite Difference Method data structure. It is a grid of floating point values, indexed by stock and time The time step index works backwards: present is the maximum index

Author:
Luigi Sgro

getPresentInterpolated

double getPresentInterpolated(double s)
Returns the value for time = 0, for any value of s within the stock range. Values of s that do not correspond to a grid point are calculated via linear interpolation

Parameters:

Returns:
